{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiong_tian_jian","speaker_name":"熊天健","listener":null,"text":"我们是在当地一家客栈的坑洞里找到他的，当时他已晕迷不醒，奄奄一息。","tone":"陈述","chapter":1,"line_start":20,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_ye_xing_shi","speaker_name":"叶星士","listener":null,"text":"他身上共有刀伤六处，虽然因为流血过多而晕迷，幸好伤不在要害，只要找个安全的地方让他静养三五天，我保证他一定恢复清醒。","tone":"陈述","chapter":1,"line_start":22,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_ying_yan_lao_qi","speaker_name":"鹰眼老七","listener":null,"text":"现在他已被送到一个绝对安全的地方休养，不经我们全体同意，连一只苍蝇都飞不进去。","tone":"认真","chapter":1,"line_start":24,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_cheng_zhong","speaker_name":"程中","listener":null,"text":"他昨天晚上已醒过一次，还喝了半碗参汤，解了一次手，等我们替他换过药后，他才睡着的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":1,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_xiao_hong_zhu","speaker_name":"萧红珠","listener":null,"text":"他解出的粪便中已没有血丝，今天早上已经能开口要水喝，还看着我笑了笑。","tone":"陈述","chapter":1,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":"char_tai_ping_wang_shi_zi","speaker_name":"太平王世子","listener":"char_ying_yan_lao_qi","text":"你说得不错，这地方实在连只苍蝇都飞不进去。","tone":"微笑","chapter":1,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"防守密室的人","listener":null,"text":"在这两个时辰中，除了萧夫人和程寨主，绝没有第三个人出入过。","tone":"严肃","chapter":1,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_tai_ping_wang_shi_zi","speaker_name":"太平王世子","listener":null,"text":"照你这么说，除非他是个隐形的人！","tone":"冷笑","chapter":1,"line_start":100,"line_end":100}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_cui_cheng","name":"崔诚","alias":[],"identity":"群英镖局趟子手","faction":"char_qun_ying_biao_ju","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"本次镖银失踪案的唯一生还者","personality":{"traits":["精明","干练","忠诚","坚毅","命大"],"speech_style":"沉稳","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":1,"line_start":10,"line_end":10,"text":"崔诚知道自己现在已变得如此重要"}]},{"id":"char_xiong_tian_jian","name":"熊天健","alias":[],"identity":"中原大侠","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"warrior"